Package: StringHelper
Title: Utilities for String Manipulation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("CHUXUAN", "ZHOU", email = "brucezcx@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a set of functions to simplify common string manipulation tasks, including reversing strings, changing case, and counting specific characters. StringHelper is designed to enhance productivity in text processing and analysis tasks.
